                {
                    "type": "html",
                    "name": "docker_guide",
                    "html": "<h3>Docker Installation Guide</h3><p><a href='/quickstart/docker' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Follow the Docker installation guide</a></p><p>This guide will walk you through running Owncast in a containerized environment.</p>"
